        dc:description           "Figure 3. Reproductive features of Amphitecna fonceti sp. nov. A ramiflorous inflorescences with several flowers per shoot B corolla mouth C strongly costate calyx D corolla showing three stamens E corolla showing the transverse fold in the throat F flower developmental stages, from bud to anthesis G fruit shape variation. Photographs by Hector Gomez Dominguez." , "Figure 2. Vegetative features of Amphitecna fonceti sp. nov. A habit B phyllotaxy C adaxial side of leaf D abaxial side of leaf. Photographs by Hector Gomez Dominguez." ;
